WorkQueuePython Namespace Reference

Python Work Queue bindings. More...

Detailed Description

Python Work Queue bindings.

The objects and methods provided by this package correspond to the native C API in work_queue.h.

The SWIG-based Python bindings provide a higher-level interface that revolves around the following objects:

  • work_queue::WorkQueue
  • work_queue::Task
